{"id":101,"name":"القارعة","transliteration":"Al-Qari'ah","type":"meccan","total_verses":11,"verses":[{"id":1,"ar":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"AlqariAAatu","de":"Das Verhängnis"},{"id":2,"ar":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"Ma alqariAAatu","de":"Was ist das Verhängnis"},{"id":3,"ar":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","tr":"Wama adraka ma alqariAAatu","de":"Und was läßt dich wissen, was das Verhängnis ist"},{"id":4,"ar":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","tr":"Yawma yakoonu alnnasu kaalfarashi almabthoothi","de":"Am Tag, da die Menschen wie flatternde Motten sein werden"},{"id":5,"ar":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","tr":"Watakoonu aljibalu kaalAAihni almanfooshi","de":"und die Berge wie zerflockte gefärbte Wolle sein werden"},{"id":6,"ar":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","tr":"Faamma man thaqulat mawazeenuhu","de":"Was nun jemanden angeht, dessen Waagschalen schwer sind"},{"id":7,"ar":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","tr":"Fahuwa fee AAeeshatin radiyatin","de":"so wird er in einem zufriedenen Leben sein"},{"id":8,"ar":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","tr":"Waamma man khaffat mawazeenuhu","de":"Was aber jemanden angeht, dessen Waagschalen leicht sind"},{"id":9,"ar":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","tr":"Faommuhu hawiyatun","de":"dessen Mutter wird ein Abgrund sein"},{"id":10,"ar":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","tr":"Wama adraka ma hiyah","de":"Und was läßt dich wissen, was das ist"},{"id":11,"ar":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","tr":"Narun hamiyatun","de":"Ein sehr heißes Feuer"}]}